title: Verizon and Sony decide to cancel the Xperia Z4v launch for unannounced reasons
text:
Verizon and Sony decide to cancel the Xperia Z4v launch for unannounced reasons 
Published By: DigitalTrends.com - Yesterday 
After months of silence, Verizon and Sony revealed that the Xperia Z4V launch will be cancelled. No reason was given, though one can assume ...
